---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import StoryStep from '../StoryStep.astro';
import Canvas from '../Canvas.astro';
import Item from '../Item.astro';
import illustration from '../../assets/early-atlanta/illustration.png';
import earlyAtlanta1 from '../../assets/early-atlanta/earlyatlanta1.png';
import still from '../../assets/early-atlanta/still.png';
---

<StoryStep title="Early Atlanta">
	<p>
		In eight years the place renamed itself twice. Terminus became Marthasville
		in 1843, then Atlanta in 1845, named for the railroad that made it: the
		Western & Atlantic.
	</p>
	<p>
		Early Atlanta was a muddy railroad boomtown of about
		2,500 people and forty saloons. The first tavern opened ten years before the
		first church.
	</p>

	<!-- Free-flow pocket: drag/resize/rotate these with ?edit. -->
	<Canvas slot="media" fill fitScale class="cluster">
		<Item
			left="2.8%"
			top="3.5%"
			width="61.7%"
			rotate={-3.6}
			phone={{ left: '1.2%', top: '9.7%', width: '64.5%', rotate: -7.6 }}
		>
			<Image src={illustration} alt="Early Atlanta illustration" />
		</Item>
		<Item
			left="15.8%"
			top="49.2%"
			width="49.6%"
			phone={{ left: '13.6%', top: '56.6%', width: '67.2%' }}
		>
			<Image src={earlyAtlanta1} alt="Early Atlanta" />
		</Item>
		<Item
			left="60.4%"
			top="5.7%"
			width="35%"
			rotate={4.4}
			phone={{ left: '50.9%', top: '6.1%', width: '47.2%', rotate: 4.4 }}
		>
			<Image src={still} alt="Early Atlanta" />
		</Item>
	</Canvas>
</StoryStep>
